{"title":"接过红旗向前走〔二首〕","authors":["周纲"],"dates":[{"year":1965,"month":8,"day":1}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"接过红旗向前走〔二首〕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"周纲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"双马石哨口礼赞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（双马石是红军在井冈山时的五大哨口之一。）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万道彩霞映绿树，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"双马石前红军路。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"望万山如浪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听松涛起伏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"涛声中，有阵阵军号，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"得得马蹄、沙沙脚步……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穿过青松林，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"踏上石板路。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席带领队伍上井冈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"百万工农刀枪举。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黑暗中华，闪出一条光明道，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"漫漫长夜，晨星耀眼天将曙！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"双马石呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青松树，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"领袖树下拴战马，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红军哨口歼匪徒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枪声犹在耳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蹄声震山谷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命航船排恶浪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千帆疾进迎日出，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"创建红色根据地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命擎天柱！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少事，难记叙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三十多年风和雨。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五星红旗映蓝天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天安门前红绸舞……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"双马石呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哨口依然，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"营垒如故。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"骏马般的双石，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"泼蹄扬鬃，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仰天长啸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"声声催人上征途！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上征途，望远处，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万里长征才走第一步。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士呵，莫将征鞍负，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"后来人，踏上红军路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"接过红旗向前走，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世纪风云擂战鼓，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乘东风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迈大步，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看前头红日喷薄出东海，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"横扫西天云和雾！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"残墙颂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（红军离开井冈山后，大井村反复被烧杀五、六次，毛主席住过的房屋也遭到破坏，只剩一堵残墙。解放后，已按原样修复，保存了这堵墙。）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"残墙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"残墙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赭色的土石，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青色的硝芒。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"留着大火余烟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"留着隐隐刀伤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象一幅革命战争的挂图，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"镶在新屋的厅堂。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"六次大火，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"草枯山光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"六次屠杀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"血洗井冈……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刀砍不碎，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民革命的理想；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火烧不垮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万载丰碑一堵墙！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只因为——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"领袖住此山庄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国有了希望，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"东方升起曙光！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"残墙呵，你是——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中流的砥柱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"真理的屏障，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火中的凤凰！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"面对残墙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无限敬仰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我思，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我想……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"英雄纪念碑的浮雕，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民大会堂的金梁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天安门白玉的华表，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中南海庄严的红墙。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新安江拦洪的大坝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鞍山高耸的厂房，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"军舰钢铁的甲板，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大寨充实的谷仓……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，残墙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它们是你今天的化身；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，残墙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你是它们昔日的模样！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"面对残墙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胸怀激荡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我歌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我唱……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"滚滚黄河水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"滔滔长江浪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命洪波远流长，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"源泉在井冈。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你是胜利反光屏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"光芒千万丈；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你是革命指路灯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"辉映四大洋！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}